BP to Flare Gases From Process Unit at Texas City Refinery

-- B y   T h e o   M u l l e n
-- 
2011-05-07T15:46:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/bp-to-flare-gases-from-process-unit-at-texas-city-refinery.html
BP Plc (BP/)  may begin restarting a process
unit today at the 475,000 barrel-a-day refinery in  Texas City ,
Texas, and flare gases, according to a regulatory  filing .  Emissions associated with the startup may occur until May
19, according to the filing with the Texas Commission on
Environmental Quality.  A  power failure  April 25 forced the plant to shut down.  To contact the reporters on this story:
